"NOT FOUND"|"Condrusi] the Condrusi, who were clientes of the Treveri, occupied the right bank of the Meuse and both banks of the Ourthe and were situated south of Aix-la-Chapelle. Their name survives in Condroz a district on the right bank of the Meuse."

